item.title: Ideas for Blogs and Projects
item.description: I am going to use this post to mark down ideas I have for blogs and projects to build - and hopefully over time they will link out to me actually doing those things! Project Ideas The parknotes project for note taking in the terminal - ongoing likely forever. Link here! Krogle - a Wordle clone using public Kroger APIs. I am an employee of corporate Kroger should I should be well equipped to do something fun/cool with the data.

item.title: About Me
item.description: Hello - I’m Parker! I am: A Lead Data Scientist at 84.51 since 2019 An incoming OMSCS Student at Georgia Tech Pretty solid at Python, but looking to learn more low level / full stack skills A husband and dog dad! Goals for this Blog and my learning I have been inspired by the classic Learn in Public blog to admit I will never be “good enough” in my own eyes to start writing and contributing back to open source and the developer community.
